{{`
We have a user used our function by a url, we need to write a email to tell him/her to try our new function.
Please extract the correct information from below information:
Email: {{email}}
Nickname: {{nickname}}
product link: {{product_link}}
Product name: {{product_name}}
Product Description: {{product_description}}

we need a json format as below:
{
	"greeting_name": str, # greeting name for the user, use in Hello {{greeting_name}}, should be one or two words.
	"product_name": str, # in 2-4 words, for the subject of the email, let the user recognize we are helping him for his products.
	"product_category_name": str, # in 1-2 words, for search for other 
	"brand_name": str, # the brand name of the product.
}
You must fill every field of the result, if the field's value is not clear, use some common phrase to fill.
output the json object only:
`}}
